><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1606180\/extras\/天地人武学.gif?t=1747757023\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>多种挑战模式：<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">真实江湖、险恶江湖、爽文江湖：从武学到词条，满足不同大侠的追求<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">从江湖虾米到独步天下：解锁传奇之路<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1606180\/extras\/爽文真实险恶.gif?t=1747757023\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">MOD编辑器，创新工坊：我们提供这个开放大世界舞台，与大侠们一起打造首款老滚5like的武侠大世界<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1606180\/extras\/MOD.gif?t=1747757023\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">庞大内容、及时更新：上线迄今已超过百更、八部大型玩法资料片！2025年我们将继续砥砺前行，用更多更好玩的内容来填充这个江湖大世界！<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">最后，白玉京工作室的所有小伙伴祝大家春节快乐！愿江湖伴你一路！<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>【关注我们】<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">官方微信好友（也可通过它加入下一站江湖II之华山论剑微信群） <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1606180\/extras\/微信群客服.png?t=1747757023\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">关注bilibili: <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1606180\/extras\/B站二维码.png?t=1747757023\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">——说武、说义、说英雄；谁是英雄？下一站江湖！                   <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">白玉京工作室 拜上<\/p>","short_description":"（“创新工坊”现已推出，当前已更新10个免费玩法资料片）《下一站江湖Ⅱ》